short_description: Kandis for Life is an entertaining, life confirming and touching documentary about a cohort of unusual Danes who finds comfort and meaning in life through their attachment to their idol, dance band star Kandis-Johnny.

Follow the Norweigan wrestling team and their journey towards the Olympics! A brutal insight in the sport as well as the athletes and their really hard work and passion to commit into this sport for a place at the podium. A honest...
